paiute reservation
nevada

5
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:50,600
loved by the buffalo could not
change growling bear's vision.

6
00:01:51,300 --> 00:01:53,400
now he sought to understand it.

7
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:56,970
new prophets came with new visions.

8
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:00,500
loved by the buffalo listened in hope.

9
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:17,100
messiah. messiah.

10
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,900
my children...

11
00:02:21,900 --> 00:02:24,900
brothers from all the nations...

12
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,500
you listen now.

13
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:32,900
i have been to the white man's heaven.

14
00:02:34,300 --> 00:02:37,500
i have seen the white man's god.

15
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:44,000
and he say to me,
one day a great spirit will come,

16
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:46,760
bring back the buffalo,

17
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:53,400
and all dead indians will
come back and live again.

18
00:02:55,900 --> 00:03:01,200
when this day comes,there
will be no more sickness.

19
00:03:01,900 --> 00:03:06,800
all indians will be strong like young men.

20
00:03:06,830 --> 00:03:08,600
be young again.

21
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:13,200
white people cannot hurt indians then.

22
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:17,700
do not tell the white people this.

23
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:20,300
follow my words.

24
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:22,760
go back to your people.

25
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:25,400
tell them to love one another.

26
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,900
do not fight.

27
00:03:27,930 --> 00:03:29,960
do not steal.

28
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,000
do not lie.

29
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:35,360
god showed me a dance

30
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,800
a dance to take to my people.

31
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,700
go home.

32
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,600
make this dance.

33
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:44,100
all indians dancing.

34
00:03:45,300 --> 00:03:47,500
good times will come.

