00:22:09,230 --> 00:22:13,270
september,1890

228
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:49,670
you must be jedediah.

229
00:22:50,190 --> 00:22:53,490
you're--you're him.

230
00:22:54,470 --> 00:22:57,300
i reckon i am.

231
00:22:59,650 --> 00:23:01,300
welcome.

232
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:03,530
welcome.

233
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:07,670
when a man gets to
a certain age,

234
00:23:07,710 --> 00:23:11,800
he wants to be close to those
folks that mean something to him.

235
00:23:12,170 --> 00:23:14,430
what family
we have left is...

236
00:23:14,460 --> 00:23:17,190
they're still
in these parts.

237
00:23:18,130 --> 00:23:20,130
but it has all
changed so much.

238
00:23:20,170 --> 00:23:25,040
makes you wonder what it's
gonna be like 100 years from now.

239
00:23:25,100 --> 00:23:27,320
bigger and faster.

240
00:23:27,370 --> 00:23:30,080
better,i suppose.

241
00:23:30,250 --> 00:23:32,270
don't know
about better.

242
00:23:37,020 --> 00:23:38,290
sir...

243
00:23:38,380 --> 00:23:42,250
do i look anything
like jedediah smith?

244
00:23:42,840 --> 00:23:46,640
there's only one
jedediah smith,son.

245
00:23:47,980 --> 00:23:49,740
but...

246
00:23:49,770 --> 00:23:52,470
let's have a look-see here.

247
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:55,140
well,if you--you put on
a few pounds

248
00:23:55,180 --> 00:23:59,080
and a few score years,
and...

249
00:23:59,250 --> 00:24:03,400
rounded it off
with a beard,i'd say...

250
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:08,250
nope. nothing like him.

251
00:24:18,310 --> 00:24:20,530
i often dream of
margaret light shines.

252
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:22,400
and you've had
no word of her?

253
00:24:22,440 --> 00:24:27,910
no. not a day goes by that
i don't wish i could see my children again.

254
00:24:30,180 --> 00:24:33,400
is she's on the reservation,
robert will find her.

255
00:24:33,450 --> 00:24:36,170
you can count on it.

