00:24:53,030 --> 00:24:55,830
and--and hold it up.

263
00:24:56,530 --> 00:24:58,720
a little higher.

264
00:24:59,180 --> 00:25:00,830
there it is!

265
00:25:00,860 --> 00:25:02,400
hold still now.

