00:25:02,450 --> 00:25:04,320
"intrepid pine ridge
police sergeants

267
00:25:04,350 --> 00:25:05,790
"old coyote
and yellow earring

268
00:25:05,830 --> 00:25:08,630
"apprehend renegade
hostiles on the warpath

269
00:25:08,670 --> 00:25:10,380
with custer's own rifles."

270
00:25:10,420 --> 00:25:12,140
yeah,that's good.

271
00:25:12,260 --> 00:25:13,740
1...

272
00:25:13,780 --> 00:25:15,300
2...

