00:43:48,430 --> 00:43:49,810
"the belligerent
old scalp-taker

448
00:43:49,850 --> 00:43:52,200
"harangued his listeners
with a brazen speech

449
00:43:52,250 --> 00:43:54,690
"in which imminent
hostilities were threatened.

450
00:43:54,720 --> 00:43:57,660
"the army can do nothing until the
murdering redskins have broken out,

451
00:43:57,700 --> 00:44:00,010
"and the young bucks have
burned a dozen ranches,

452
00:44:00,040 --> 00:44:01,900
and slaughtered a score
of women and children--"

453
00:44:01,940 --> 00:44:03,650
general miles' orders
are quite specific.

454
00:44:03,690 --> 00:44:06,420
to offer protection,
and maintain control and discipline.

455
00:44:06,450 --> 00:44:10,320
so we're all just
expected to sit here?

456
00:44:17,580 --> 00:44:20,620
in the meantime,you are
directed not to force any issue

457
00:44:20,660 --> 00:44:22,470
that might result
in an outbreak.

458
00:44:22,500 --> 00:44:24,250
discretion,mr. royer.

459
00:44:24,280 --> 00:44:27,500
if you and the other civilian au
horities had demonstrated as much,

460
00:44:27,550 --> 00:44:31,720
the seventh would not
be here now to enforce order.

461
00:45:14,500 --> 00:45:16,270
what's going on?

462
00:45:16,290 --> 00:45:18,940
word is sitting bull's
headed this way

463
00:45:18,970 --> 00:45:22,040
to join the renegades
in the badlands.

464
00:45:22,070 --> 00:45:24,800
we'll be read for him.

465
00:45:25,780 --> 00:45:27,990
i caution you
against any supply trips

466
00:45:28,040 --> 00:45:30,510
through standing rock
in the next few days,mr. wheeler.

467
00:45:30,540 --> 00:45:31,600
why is that?

468
00:45:31,640 --> 00:45:34,240
general miles has
authorized sitting bull's arrest.

469
00:45:34,270 --> 00:45:36,790
wouldn't it be better
to wait till ration day?

470
00:45:36,830 --> 00:45:37,990
the fewer of
his people around,

471
00:45:38,030 --> 00:45:40,350
less cause there'll be
for a disagreement.

472
00:45:40,400 --> 00:45:43,930
sitting bull's actions
require his immediate apprehension.

473
00:45:44,010 --> 00:45:46,650
well,could be
just rumor.

474
00:45:46,680 --> 00:45:48,930
whatever the people
of the press are telling you.

475
00:45:48,960 --> 00:45:52,120
i provide you this information
with regard to your own safety,mr. wheeler.

476
00:45:52,150 --> 00:45:55,760
what you wish
to do with it
is not my concern.

477
00:46:08,780 --> 00:46:10,260
take it.

478
00:46:10,340 --> 00:46:12,250
i can't.

479
00:46:12,330 --> 00:46:15,470
you are false to your people
if you do not wear the ghost shirt.

480
00:46:15,510 --> 00:46:18,310
this way is the way
to death,red lance.

481
00:46:18,340 --> 00:46:20,610
maybe we can
find our own road.

482
00:46:20,630 --> 00:46:23,740
maybe we can
find our own
destiny again.

483
00:46:29,030 --> 00:46:30,940
what are you doing?

484
00:46:31,020 --> 00:46:33,820
you have
too many wasichu ways.

485
00:46:36,700 --> 00:46:38,650
you even think
like a wasichu!

486
00:46:38,700 --> 00:46:41,930
you play the savage
for money,red lance!not me!

487
00:48:19,150 --> 00:48:21,400
indian police.

488
00:48:31,750 --> 00:48:33,860
what do you want here?

489
00:48:34,400 --> 00:48:36,210
you are my prisoner.

490
00:48:36,250 --> 00:48:39,100
you must
go into the agency.

491
00:48:50,960 --> 00:48:54,790
we were warriors together

492
00:48:56,290 --> 00:48:59,360
now you do the white man's bidding

493
00:49:03,970 --> 00:49:05,840
let go of me!

494
00:49:11,300 --> 00:49:12,230
coming through!

495
00:49:18,000 --> 00:49:19,660
keep moving!

496
00:49:21,450 --> 00:49:23,990
sitting bull
is under arrest.

497
00:49:24,920 --> 00:49:26,480
do not take him!

498
00:49:26,510 --> 00:49:28,430
protect our chief

499
00:49:29,810 --> 00:49:30,580
no!

500
00:49:31,630 --> 00:49:32,920
come with us.

501
00:49:32,960 --> 00:49:35,280
white hair mclaughlin
only wants to talk with you.

502
00:49:35,320 --> 00:49:38,310
don't listen to
these troublemakers.

503
00:49:39,070 --> 00:49:39,850
come on.

504
00:50:34,460 --> 00:50:39,270
december 24,1890

505
00:50:43,490 --> 00:50:46,740
move it to the right
a little more.

506
00:51:02,040 --> 00:51:04,680
apart from a few
minor skirmishes,

507
00:51:04,720 --> 00:51:08,140
most of the fugitives have
been persuaded to return peaceably.

508
00:51:08,180 --> 00:51:10,570
hunger can be a powerful
inducement to surrender.

509
00:51:10,610 --> 00:51:13,280
we've still got thousands
holed up in the badlands,

510
00:51:13,310 --> 00:51:17,760
and no telling how many of sitting
bull's people racing
to meet them.

511
00:51:17,800 --> 00:51:20,770
our principal concern
is chief big foot.

512
00:51:20,810 --> 00:51:23,810
abandoned his camp on the
cheyenne river several days ago.

513
00:51:24,300 --> 00:51:26,080
lieutenant colonel sumner
intercepted him,

514
00:51:26,130 --> 00:51:27,930
and demanded
his immediate return.

515
00:51:27,960 --> 00:51:30,080
big foot
promised to do so,

